After creating the container in Dockerfile (apache), proceed with the following steps

cd /etc/apache2/sites-available

vi gammaz.hm.conf 

  paste these following lines inside the file,
  
  ServerName gammaz.hm.com
  ServerAlias gammaz.hm.com
  
  change "DocumentRoot /var/www/html" to "DocumentRoot /var/www/gammaz.hm"
  
service apache2 start

a2ensite gammaz.hm.conf

a2dissite 000-default.conf

service apache2 reload 

and if you type in localhost on your host's browser, u should be able to see the mess.txt file

NOTE: use "docker run -p 80:80 ......" while running the container to specify 80 as the exposed port 
